entries.journal_entry_description: Captain Dool has some tasks that he'd like you to complete for him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Captain Dool wants you to find out more about Greck. See if you can find any information from his men.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Another of my informants got something. A file was stolen from CorSec recently with Greck's information in it. It was taken by the Chirq Council for some reason.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Captain Dool wants you to hit a Chirq Council outpost and see if they have the file on Olag Greck. Get the file and return it to Captain Dool.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: I want you to take that report to one of our City Councilmen, Lyman Zavala. He'll know what to do from here. Thanks for your help.
